{"serial": "21026", "department_serial": 20, "code": "MA2022", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Probability and Statistics", "ch": "機率與統計"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Lee, Yen-Chi"], "ch": ["李彥奇"]}, "credits": 4, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 2, "session": ["1", "2"]}, "loc": {"building": "M", "room": "327"}}, {"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["1", "2"]}, "loc": {"building": "M", "room": "327"}}], "isRequired": true, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 50, "department": {"ch": "數學系", "en": "Department of Mathematics"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 30, "selected": 0, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "本課程旨在直觀且精確地介紹機率論及其在數學、應用數學、科學、工程等相關領域中的應用。課程內容將涵蓋機率的基本概念、隨機變數、多元隨機變數、大數法則及中心極限定理。", "en": "This course aims to intuitively and precisely introduce probability theory and its applications in related fields such as mathematics, applied mathematics, science, and engineering. The course content will cover fundamental concepts of probability, random variables, multivariate random variables, the law of large numbers, and the central limit theorem."}, "outline": {"ch": "一、樣本空間與機率\n二、離散型隨機變數\n三、連續型隨機變數\n四、隨機變數進階主題 (轉換、條件期望、隨機變數和)\n五、極限定理 (大數法則、中央極限定理)\n六、貝氏推論與經典推論 (if time permits)", "en": "1. Sample Space and Probability\n2. Discrete Random Variables\n3. Continuous Random Variables\n4. Further Topics on Random Variables (Functions of RVs, Conditional Expectation, Random Sum of RVs)\n5. Limit Theorems\n6. Introduction to Bayesian and Classical Statistical Inference (if time permits)"}, "textbook": {"ch": "1. “Introduction to Probability (2nd Edition),“ by Dimitri P. Bertsekas and John N. Tsitsiklis\n2. “Mathematical Statistics with Applications (7th Edition, 2008),“ by Dennis D. Wackerly, William Mendenhall III, and Richard L. Scheaffer (前六章)\n3. “Fundamentals of Probability with Stochastic Processes (4th Edition, 2018)“,